# [DNSOP](../wg/dnsop.html)

## Summary
The DNSOP Working Group met at IETF 125 to discuss the status of active drafts, recent RFC publications, and several new proposals. Key topics included automated delegation management via DDNS, updates to DNS data ranking rules, operational considerations for protective DNS (PDS) operators, and techniques to mitigate amplification attacks using large wildcard records. 

## Key Discussion Points

